Test Title: Enter valid values in all fields
Steps:
1-Go to System Settings > Documentation Categories > Add New Categories
2-Enter Arabic Name < 100 char. in Name in Arabic
3-Enter English name < 100 char. in Name in English
4-Select a valid value from Category type
5-Select a valid value from Status
6-Click on Add Category button
Description: Verify that the category can be added successfully when all fields are filled correctly.
Preconditions:
1-User logged in
2-User in Add category page
Test Data:
Name in Arabic:  تصنيف المنتجات النهائية الجاهزة للبيع
Name in English: Classification of finished products ready for sale
Category Type: Main Category
Status: active
Expected Result: Category is added successfully and displayed in the Category List.
Actual Result: Category added successfully and redirected to category list
Comments: The form works correctly and saves valid data; no validation issues found.
